This directory containts interactive examples of running Flasher simulations using CLSim.

1. Before you start, make sure that you are running on an interactive GPU job with a singularity container and the respective pone_offline environment loaded.

2. We will need to import pone_offline modules in some of these scripts, so make sure to symlink them to this directory first by
$ ln -s $PONESRCDIR/<directory needed>

3. Then simply run one of the test scripts with
$ python <test_script.py>
